Setup for the test case presented in Bordbar et al.(2020) article.

For more details see "An extended weighted-sum-of-gray-gases 
model to account for all CO2‐H2O molar fraction ratios in 
thermal radiation".
doi: https://doi.org/10.1016/j.icheatmasstransfer.2019.104400

Replace the functions present in RTS_functions.f90 with those present in user_functions.f90
